Lady was nice to my daughter.
DVD didn't work, I asked for the Deluxe which is supposed to include a shampoo, haircut and style.
She washed and conditioned my daughters hair and cut it like I asked.
"Styling" involved her putting a ton of glitter gel in my kid's hair and then turning on the blow dryer for (literally) one minute.
I purchased shampoo and conditioner from them and all told I spent $70.
We will not be coming back.

